dc_title_s: 1:100,000 Quadrangle Polygon Boundaries: Russian River Watershed, California, 1996
dc_description_s: This layer shows the areas of the USGS 1:100,000 quadrangle boundary maps that are within the watershed boundaries of the Russian River basin.This shapefile contains the boundaries of the 100k quadrangles of California to be used for geographic reference.
